    <p>The datasets analysed in this study are available in GEO with accession numbers: GSE113734 (<xref rid="B7" ref-type="bibr">7</xref>), GSE114685 (<xref rid="B8" ref-type="bibr">8</xref>), GSE102956 (<xref rid="B9" ref-type="bibr">9</xref>), GSE126562 (<xref rid="B10" ref-type="bibr">10</xref>), GSE130521 (<xref rid="B11" ref-type="bibr">11</xref>). These datasets were derived from the following public domain resource: <ext-link xlink:href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo" ext-link-type="uri">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/geo</ext-link>. The analyses were performed with <monospace>CRISPRroots</monospace> version 1.1. The <monospace>CRISPRroots</monospace> software is freely available via <ext-link xlink:href="https://rth.dk/resources/crispr" ext-link-type="uri">https://rth.dk/resources/crispr</ext-link> and on GitHub via <ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/RTH-tools/crisprroots" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/RTH-tools/crisprroots</ext-link>. The software comes with a tutorial on how to reproduce the results presented in this article.</p>
